Convolution is also defined in mathlib and its basic properties are proved.
EXAMPLES: -/

-- QUOTE:
open_locale convolution

example  (f : ℝ → ℝ) (g : ℝ → ℝ) :
  f ⋆ g = λ x, ∫ t, (f t) * (g (x - t)) :=
rfl
